    <h1 class="main">From James Lovell</h1>
    
    <div class="docbody">
     <h2>Confidential</h2>
     <div class="opener">
      <table class="salutationBlock">
        <tr>
		<td class="salutationRight">Tuesday 28th. of Sepr. 1779 in Continuance</td>
	      </tr>
      </table>
     </div>
     <p>Mr. Jay having resigned the Chair on account of other public Engagements, the Honble. Mr. Huntingdon was Elected President of Congress. Tomorrow, will be chosen Secretaries for</p>
     <table class="bodytext" id="PJA08d128t1">
     <tr class="head">
	      <td>France</td>
	      <td></td>
	      <td>Spain</td>
	      <td></td>
	      <td>and the Negociator</td>
	    </tr>
     <tr>
	      <td class="text">{nominated</td>
	      <td></td>
	      <td></td>
	      <td></td>
	      <td></td>
	    </tr>
     <tr>
	      <td class="text">Peter Scull</td>
	      <td class="brace" rowspan="3"><img src="images/brace-open-trans.png" alt="{" class="brace" style="height: 3.5em; width: 17px;"/></td>
	      <td class="text">Mr. Carmichael</td>
	      <td class="brace" rowspan="3"><img src="images/brace-open-trans.png" alt="{" class="brace" style="height: 3.5em; width: 17px;"/></td>
	      <td class="text">Jno. Trumbull<a class="ptr" href="#PJA08d128n1" id="PJA08d128n1-ptr">1</a></td>
	    </tr>
     <tr>
	      <td class="text">by</td>
	      <td class="text">by</td>
